'''"Tauntaun Feathers A1"''' was the name of a [[Datacard/Legends|datacard]] created by [[Kyle Katarn]] and his [[Padawan/Legends|apprentice]], [[Jaden Korr]], reporting the investigation on the disturbance in [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] on [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]].

[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] later donated this report to the [[New Republic Historical Archive]].

